name: Zeto
overview: The Zeto platform is the first multi-vendor management solution for the global commercial refrigeration industry. The company are bringing a ground-breaking solution to the market to transform the industry and transform the way refrigeration equipment is managed. Zeto is an Irish based company that design hardware and software to manage refrigeration equipment. Zeto was incorporated in 2011 by Stephen and Michael Slattery. Zeto is led by Stephen Slattery as part of an outstanding management team combining deep expertise across the refrigeration and IT industries. Zeto sell hardware and software licenses to the global refrigeration industry from their head office in Cork by demonstrating the benefits of the platform to the refrigeration users. Refrigeration users then specify compliance with the platform as part of their new equipment tendering requirements. Zeto’s cloud-based platform provides complete multi-vendor management capability that will enable a new era of intelligent refrigeration management for refrigeration users, maintenance companies and equipment providers.
